WHATS NEW IN SCRIPTALICIOUS
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

In the last non-bugfix (1.03) release;

  - YAML config file support.  Do your getopt() and YAML::Load() in
    one pass!  See getconf() in the man page.

  - New timer utility functions start_timer(), show_delta(),
    show_elapsed()

COMING SOON TO SCRIPTALICIOUS:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  - include the default YAML configuration file in your POD via
    Pod::Constants!
